[/list]
[/list]
[size=3][u][b]First-time setup (Configuration tab)[/b][/u][/size]

1) Game Folder
[list][list]
[*] Click Set next to “Game Folder” and select your X4.exe. Typical paths:
[list]
[*] Steam: [b]C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\X4 Foundations\X4.exe[/b]
[*] GOG/Epic: wherever you installed X4
[/list]
[/list]
[/list]
2) Save file
[list][list]
[*] Click Set next to “Game Save Path” and choose a save [b].xml.gz[/b]. Typical path:
[list]
[*] Steam: [b]%USERPROFILE%\Documents\Egosoft\X4\<player-id>\save\quicksave.xml.gz[/b]
[*] GOG/Epic: [b]%USERPROFILE%\Documents\Egosoft\X4\save\quicksave.xml.gz[/b]
[/list]
[/list]
[/list]
3) Load data
[list][list]
[*] Click “Reload Data” for the Game Folder to import base game data (wares, factions, etc.).
[*] Click “Reload Data” for the Save Path to import your transactions.
[*] When data is present, the other tabs become enabled.
[/list]
[/list]
4) Optional settings
[list][list]
[*] Load Only Game Language: speeds up loading by using your game language only.
[*] Theme: System, Light, or Dark.
[/list]
[/list]
